  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 180°C (350°F).",
    "In a large mixing bowl, combine cornmeal, chickpeas, cocoa powder, almonds, Greek yogurt, flaxseeds, minced garlic, olive oil, salt, and pepper. Mix well until all ingredients are fully incorporated.",
    "Divide the mixture into two portions and press each portion onto an oven-safe dish lined with parchment paper or aluminum foil to prevent sticking.",
    "Bake for 30-40 minutes or until golden brown on top.",
    "Let it cool slightly before serving. Serve as a side dish or enjoy alone as a protein-packed dinner option."
